label: Sorting Algorithm (Bubble Sort)
Sorting Algorithm (Insertion Sort)
code:
numbers = [64, 34, 25, 12, 22, 11, 90]
length = len(numbers)

for i in range(1, length):
    key = numbers[i]
    j = i - 1
    while j >= 0 and key < numbers[j]:
        numbers[j + 1] = numbers[j]
        j -= 1
    numbers[j + 1] = key

print(numbers)
